                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-970-18661022 t18661022-970-punishment-75"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">ADJOURNED TO MONDAY, NOVEMBER</hi> 19, 1866.</p>
